<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 14:07:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战斗或逃跑：哈马斯袭击后，这些以色列人逃离该国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fight-or-flight-after-hamas-attacked-these-israelis-fled-the-country/0000018b-3876-d450-a3af-797e47690000</link><description>从罗马到塞浦路斯和希腊：除了数千名在战争爆发时回国的以色列人之外，还有许多人前往国外，因为以色列正面临着最困难的时期之一 ■ 大多数人都有年幼的孩子，有能力预订机票而不必担心价格</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 13:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fight-or-flight-after-hamas-attacked-these-israelis-fled-the-country/0000018b-3876-d450-a3af-797e47690000</guid></item><item><title>向以色列空运、约旦轰炸机、两艘航母：美国向中东部署更多部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-16/ty-article/airlift-to-israel-bombers-in-jordan-two-carriers-u-s-deploying-more-forces-to-mideast/0000018b-385d-d450-a3af-795de1010000</link><description>开源飞行跟踪和卫星图像显示，该地区部署了先进的武器、防空系统以及数十架战斗轰炸机、情报收集平台和重型货运飞机，试图阻止伊朗和真主党在以色列北部开辟第二条战线</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 13:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-16/ty-article/airlift-to-israel-bombers-in-jordan-two-carriers-u-s-deploying-more-forces-to-mideast/0000018b-385d-d450-a3af-795de1010000</guid></item><item><title>我们犹太人需要听到穆斯林领导人谴责哈马斯的暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-jews-need-to-hear-muslim-leaders-denounce-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-3777-d450-a3af-7f7fc0660000</link><description>当务之急是与巴勒斯坦人和那些与我们有着同样恐惧的阿拉伯和穆斯林世界的人们找到共同的事业。我们需要从阿拉伯领导人、伊玛目和穆斯林学者那里听到，这是对真正伊斯兰教的耻辱</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 13:30:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-jews-need-to-hear-muslim-leaders-denounce-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-3777-d450-a3af-7f7fc0660000</guid></item><item><title>被绑架以色列人的家人会见内塔尼亚胡，却发现身份不明的家人支持总理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/hostage-relatives-suspected-to-have-been-planted-in-meeting-with-pm-to-bolster-his-policy/0000018b-37af-dc99-a1db-3fefa6ed0000</link><description>“我们需要停止这种发牢骚的行为。我们需要赢得战争。”出席人质家属与以色列总理会面的未经证实的亲属说道，这引起了其他人的轩然大波。</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 12:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/hostage-relatives-suspected-to-have-been-planted-in-meeting-with-pm-to-bolster-his-policy/0000018b-37af-dc99-a1db-3fefa6ed0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯绑架了她的女儿：“我很抱歉，但我不相信上帝存在”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-believe-god-exists-if-he-does-why-are-my-daughters-in-gaza/0000018b-3810-df29-a5ab-fe7f29520000</link><description>周六，Maayan Zin 的两个女儿（分别为 8 岁和 15 岁）与她们的父亲、他的伴侣以及伴侣的儿子一起在纳哈尔奥兹。她从姐姐发给她的一张照片中得知他们被绑架了 ■ 《国土报》与被绑架以色列人家人的对话</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 11:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-believe-god-exists-if-he-does-why-are-my-daughters-in-gaza/0000018b-3810-df29-a5ab-fe7f29520000</guid></item><item><title>数百名法律专家表示，哈马斯的致命暴行构成“国际种族灭绝罪”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/hamas-deadly-rampage-constitutes-crime-of-genocide-hundreds-of-legal-experts-say/0000018b-37d1-d450-a3af-7fddda070000</link><description>在一封公开信中，领先的法律学者声称，“由于这些广泛而可怕的行为似乎是为了全部或部分摧毁一个民族群体——以色列人——而进行的，因此它们很可能构成国际种族灭绝罪”</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 11:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/hamas-deadly-rampage-constitutes-crime-of-genocide-hundreds-of-legal-experts-say/0000018b-37d1-d450-a3af-7fddda070000</guid></item><item><title>拜登希望避免以色列局势升级，而不是加入战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-wants-to-avoid-escalation-in-israel-not-join-a-war/0000018b-37a6-d051-a1cb-3fffe2ae0000</link><description>美国支持以色列以及对加沙哈马斯采取合法军事反应的信息不应被误解为美国总统乔·拜登希望加入中东战争，或愿意忽视巴勒斯坦平民的苦难</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 10:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-wants-to-avoid-escalation-in-israel-not-join-a-war/0000018b-37a6-d051-a1cb-3fffe2ae0000</guid></item><item><title>皮特·戴维森在《周六夜现场》的忧郁开场中反思了以色列与哈马斯的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/pete-davidson-reflects-on-israel-hamas-war-in-somber-opening-of-saturday-night-live/0000018b-37b1-dc99-a1db-3ff1b3890000</link><description>戴维森说：“我的心与本周生活被毁的所有人同在”，并在网上得到了热烈的回应</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 09:48:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/pete-davidson-reflects-on-israel-hamas-war-in-somber-opening-of-saturday-night-live/0000018b-37b1-dc99-a1db-3ff1b3890000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯看不见的受害者：在以色列的泰国工人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-unseen-victims-of-hamas-thai-workers-in-israel/0000018b-333b-dff1-a5eb-ffffa2b60000</link><description>暴乱发生之前，有超过 5,000 名泰国人在加沙附近的以色列农业部门工作。超过 20 人被哈马斯杀害 - 那些逃脱的人试图在残酷的现实中生存 ■ 一位农民说：“如果你不工作，你就必须离开”</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 09:28:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-unseen-victims-of-hamas-thai-workers-in-israel/0000018b-333b-dff1-a5eb-ffffa2b60000</guid></item><item><title>外国外交官称，有关释放部分以色列人质的人道主义协议的谈判正在进行中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomats-talks-on-humanitarian-deal-for-release-of-some-israeli-hostages-ongoing/0000018b-3753-da5e-abef-bf775eb30000</link><description>消息人士称，目前尚不清楚是否以及何时达成协议。以色列政治领导层对解决方案仍模棱两可</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 09:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomats-talks-on-humanitarian-deal-for-release-of-some-israeli-hostages-ongoing/0000018b-3753-da5e-abef-bf775eb30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加大GPS干扰力度，阻止真主党和哈马斯无人机袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-ramps-up-gps-jamming-to-thwart-hezbollah-hamas-drone-attacks/0000018b-3784-d051-a1cb-3fdfdfe10000</link><description>然而，以色列的干扰也会扰乱以色列国防军的火箭警告应用程序 ■ 美国研究人员最近在以色列北部基地对一个强大的 GPS 干扰器进行了地理定位</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 08:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-ramps-up-gps-jamming-to-thwart-hezbollah-hamas-drone-attacks/0000018b-3784-d051-a1cb-3fdfdfe10000</guid></item><item><title>军队将撤离黎巴嫩边境附近28个社区的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/israelis-in-28-communities-near-lebanon-border-to-be-evacuated-by-army/0000018b-3734-d051-a1cb-3fff81450000</link><description>随着黎巴嫩和以色列之间的紧张局势升级，以色列北部的居民将被疏散到政府资助的酒店和宾馆</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 07:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/israelis-in-28-communities-near-lebanon-border-to-be-evacuated-by-army/0000018b-3734-d051-a1cb-3fff81450000</guid></item><item><title>真主党不是哈马斯，所以以色列以不同的方式打击他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-isnt-hamas-so-israel-fights-them-differently/0000018b-34e4-d450-a3af-7dfcca110000</link><description>哈马斯的袭击使以色列陷入了一场全面战争，以彻底摧毁哈马斯，但由于黎巴嫩真主党，以色列仍然可以进行一场更加克制的冲突，而不必失控</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 06:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-isnt-hamas-so-israel-fights-them-differently/0000018b-34e4-d450-a3af-7dfcca110000</guid></item><item><title>真主党试图阻止以色列入侵加沙，北部紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/tensions-rise-in-the-north-as-hezbollah-tries-to-deter-israel-from-invading-gaza/0000018b-34d8-ddcb-a7bf-b7db6f590000</link><description>真主党正在以牙还牙，考验以色列的耐心，重点关注以色列在加沙地带的下一步行动。尽管如此，这并不是现状，而且存在相当大的误判风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 05:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/tensions-rise-in-the-north-as-hezbollah-tries-to-deter-israel-from-invading-gaza/0000018b-34d8-ddcb-a7bf-b7db6f590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：至少199人被哈马斯绑架，291名士兵被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-live/israel-prepares-for-ground-invasion-biden-big-mistake-to-reoccupy-gaza/0000018b-364f-dc99-a1db-3fcf1ae10000</link><description>埃及声称以色列同意临时停火，但以色列否认 ■ 黎巴嫩媒体声称美国向哈马斯提供援助，以换取释放人质 ■ 一名以色列人在早上的火箭袭击中受伤 ■ 自哈马斯袭击以来，已有 1,300 多名以色列人丧生，至少 2,750 人加沙人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 05:22:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-16/ty-article-live/israel-prepares-for-ground-invasion-biden-big-mistake-to-reoccupy-gaza/0000018b-364f-dc99-a1db-3fcf1ae10000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对巴勒斯坦裔美国男孩被谋杀感到“恶心”：“可怕的仇恨行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-sickened-over-palestinian-american-boys-murder-horrific-act-of-hate/0000018b-365a-da5e-abef-bf7f485a0000</link><description>以色列和加沙战争期间，一名 6 岁儿童因伊斯兰教信仰在伊利诺伊州遭到袭击，被刺死，他的母亲受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 02:54:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-16/ty-article/.premium/biden-sickened-over-palestinian-american-boys-murder-horrific-act-of-hate/0000018b-365a-da5e-abef-bf7f485a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府各部委的崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-16/ty-article-opinio